setCharset

public void setCharset(String charset)
Set the character set that will be used to encode and (maybe) decode messages received within this session. Messages sent will always be encoded using the given character set, but received messages that specify a character set in the message header will be decoded according to that character set. If this method is not called, or the given charset is null, the default encoding character set is specified by PDS.encoding and the default decoding character set is specified by PDS.decoding.

Parameters:
charset - the character set to use for this session (null to use the default encoding and decoding character sets).
